	{
		sendPrivateMessage(sender, "\n=~======================~~~=========,,,,,,:~~====++++????????????????????++=::~= \n=~==================================,,,,,::~~~===++++???????????????????+++=~~~~ \n=~===========~======================,,.,,::~~~~===+++???????????????????+++=~~~~ \n=~==============+==================~,.,,,::~~~~====+++?????????????????++++=~~~= \n=~========+=====+?=================~..,,::~~~=======+++++????+???????+?++++==:~~ \n=~========+=====+?=================:..,,:~~~~========+++++++??++++++++++++++=:~~ \n=========~+=====+++============:,,:=..,,:~~~~=~~~~~~========+++++++++========:== \n=========++=====++?==========:.,:::~..,::~::~~~::,,,,:::~~~======~~:::::~~~==~== \n========+++==++=++?++======~..,::~::..,:~::::::::::,,,,:::~===~~::::::::~~~~=~== \n========++++=+???????+?+==,.,:~=~=~:,,,~~::::,:::,,,,,,,,:=+??=::,,,,,,,::~~=:~= \n~=======??+I?????+=~~..:II++~~~~~=~,,,,~~~~:,,.:,...,..,,~+????:,,,..,,,:::~=~== \n~=======+??II??+~:,.,..=77?+++==~~,:,,:~~===~~~~~==~:::,~=+??I?~,,:,,,::~=~===== \n~=====+?IIIII?+:,,,,.:~I77I??++==~::,.:~~=====~:~~~:~~====+??I?++:::~=====+++=== \n======??IIII?+=,,..~=?I777IIII?+==::,~~~~==++????+++++====+?II?+++??++++????+=== \n======+????I??7~:.:.??I77I??II??+,:::::~~==++??????+++===++?II?+++??????????+=== \n======+++?????I7?=~,III77?+::=I?,.,,~,:~~==+++++?+++~~~=++??II??+=++????????+=== \n=======+????+?II77IIII77II~.:=I?:..~~::~~~====++++=~~=+==+???II??+~=++?+?++++=== \n=====+==++++==+?II77??I77I?I?7I?=..,~:~~~~~~~~===~~=~==~~=++????+=+~===++++===== \n======+=====++=+IIII7++????77I?+:.....:~~::::~:::::::,::,,::~~~::~~~::~~~~~~~=== \n=======+++====+?????II~~:II??++=......:~~::::::::::~:,,,,,,,,,,,,~~~:,,:::::~=== \n========++~?+=~==+++=~~=+??I=++,......,~~~:::::::::::,,,,,,,,,,,:~~~::,,:::~~=== \n================~~~:::::==+++==.,......:~~~~~~~::,.,,,,,,,,,,,::~~:::::::~~~==== \n==========+==~=~=~~~~~=~~=~====..,.....::~~~:~===~~~~::,,,,,,,:~~~~:~~~~~~~~==== \n==============~~~~~~~~~~===++=.,:.,.....:::~~~~=~==~~~~~~::